Monitor Usage Statistics for Einstein Discovery for Reports

Einstein Discovery for Reports monitors usage statistics in real time. You can view the usage statistics in your org.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in Lightning Experience
Available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.
USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To monitor Einstein Discovery for Reports usage statistics: Customize Application

To view usage statistics:
From Setup, enter Discovery.
Under Einstein Discovery and Einstein Discovery for Reports, select Usage.

Times and dates are based on your orgâ€™s default time zone.

Number of analysis created today Total number of analyses created in your org since 12:00am today.
Number of analysis currently being created Total number of analyses that are currently being run in your org.
